entity_type_and_legal_name_intro: Enter your entity type and the legal name of your company. You can find this info on your <einLink>FEIN assignment form (Form CP575)</einLink>. We need this to file and pay your taxes correctly.
federal_ein_description: Your company's Federal Employer Identification Number (EIN). If you don't have one, please <applyLink>apply online.</applyLink>
taxpayer_type_description: Some common types are Sole Prop, LLC, and S-Corp.
federal_filing_form_description: To learn more about the different Federal Tax Form filings for payroll, please review the <irsLink>IRS website.</irsLink>
legal_entity_name_description: Make sure this is the legal name of the company, not your DBA.
